name: Lorenzo Francisca
bio: Don't judge a book by it's cover. I may look disheveled. I may have an overgrown beard, and not showered for the past month but don't dismiss me just like that. I am a multi-millionare from Wall Street, a pure master in their craft, a true professional in the field of finance. Come and work with Francisca Paradisical Finances, true Italian financial genius
